Package: shinyelectron
Title: Export Shiny Applications as Desktop Applications using Electron
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("James Joseph", "Balamuta",
            email = "james.balamuta@gmail.com", 
            role = c("aut", "cre"),
            comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2826-8458")
           )
    )
Description: Provides tools to export Shiny applications as standalone desktop
    applications using Electron. This allows Shiny applications to run as native
    desktop applications on Windows, Mac, and Linux without requiring users to
    have R installed.
License: AGPL (>= 3)
URL: https://r-pkg.thecoatlessprofessor.com/shinyelectron/, https://github.com/coatless-rpkg/shinyelectron
BugReports: https://github.com/coatless-rpkg/shinyelectron/issues
